data.description: Three bedroom brick rancher with recently updated kitchen and bathrooms. Main level features a large family room, formal dining, kitchen with stainless appliances, primary bedroom with half bath, 2 bedrooms and hall bath. A spacious screen porch may be the best room in the house.  Just off the family room, you can enjoy views of the mountains and cattle grazing in the pasture just behind the property. The porch affords room for a dining and sitting area.  If you like to tinker in a garden, this property is already set up for your vegetable garden in the back yard. The lower level has plentiful storage for all your holiday decor, garden tools and overflow large pantry items. The one car garage and the laundry are in the basement level. The landscaping throughout the property features river rock and mature plantings. This is your chance to live out int he countryside but be in close proximity to all the amenities of town. Knoxville, Tri-Cities or Sevier County are within an hours drive.
